[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":502},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F":479,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F":488},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F11\u002F01\u002Flearn-hexo-33-updating-next-theme\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":462,"date":463,"description":18,"extension":464,"lang":465,"meta":466,"navigation":467,"path":468,"readingMinutes":469,"seo":470,"standalone":471,"stem":472,"tags":473,"tldr":476,"updated":476,"url":477,"__hash__":478},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F33-試著學-Hexo-番外篇之更新-NexT-主題.md","(33)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 NexT 主題","60919",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":456},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,35,38,41,57,60,63,72,75,84,94,107,110,125,129,140,149,156,162,165,243,246,249,252,304,307,427,435,438,446,449,452],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來這一篇將會介紹如何更新 NexT 主題與介紹 Hexo5 之後的 NexT 之後有什麼樣的改變。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"next","NexT",[16,24,25,26,30,31,34],{},"在前一個章節我們有介紹到 Hexo5 之後的主題可以支援 npm 安裝，而在這邊 NexT 也已經可以在 npm 下載，透過這種方式最主要好處在於「更新」，在原本的作法我們都是透過 ",[27,28,29],"code",{},"git clone"," 的方式回來，因此若要更新主題就必須使用 ",[27,32,33],{},"git pull"," 等方式更新合併，但這個方式其實並不是那麼好用，一方面主題必須加入版本控制，另一方面我們若要做一些調整其實就相對很不方便（例如版型的小調整）。",[16,36,37],{},"因此這邊我們將會透過 npm 來安裝 NexT 囉。",[16,39,40],{},"請在剛剛建立好的 Hexo5 專案輸入以下指令",[42,43,48],"pre",{"className":44,"code":45,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","npm install --save hexo-theme-next\n","cmd","",[27,49,50],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,52,55],"span",{"class":53,"line":54},"line",1,[51,56,45],{},[16,58,59],{},"你也可以直接輸入以下任一指令",[16,61,62],{},"安裝最新版本：",[42,64,66],{"className":44,"code":65,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"npm install hexo-theme-next@latest\n",[27,67,68],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,69,70],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,71,65],{},[16,73,74],{},"指定特定版本：",[42,76,78],{"className":44,"code":77,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"npm install hexo-theme-next@8.0.0\n",[27,79,80],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,81,82],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,83,77],{},[16,85,86,87,89,90,93],{},"(當然，你還是可以使用 ",[27,88,29],{}," 的方式，如果你會有需要大量客製化建議改走原本的建立方式，因為檔案會建立在原本的 ",[27,91,92],{},"themes\u002Fnext"," 底下。)",[16,95,96,97,100,101,106],{},"在這邊先講一個簡單觀念，npm 下載的檔案都會在 ",[27,98,99],{},"node_modules"," 底下，這代表什麼呢？在前面「",[102,103,105],"a",{"href":104},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200917\u002F636983586\u002F","試著學 Hexo - 認識 Hexo 目錄結構","」有簡單說到這個資料夾是放置「Hexo 所需要運作的套件暫存處」，因此在這個資料夾底下我們都不會去動到甚至修改，因為這資料夾都是透過 npm 來還原，使用這個方式的好處在於更新與一些設置的方便性，後面介紹你會更有感覺。",[16,108,109],{},"否則在原本作法上，更新就如同前面說的一樣「很麻煩」，而且在版本控制上時常會踩雷，例如：themes 底下的主題無法加入版本控制，必須刪除主題底下的隱藏資料夾 .git 才能夠一併加入到版本控制內，否則在轉移電腦使用時會出現問題。",[16,111,112,113,116,117,120,121,124],{},"當你輸入完畢之後，一樣到 ",[27,114,115],{},"hexo\u002F_config.yml"," 搜尋 ",[27,118,119],{},"theme:"," 並改成 ",[27,122,123],{},"theme: next"," 就可以套用主題囉。",[12,126,128],{"id":127},"新版-next-特色","新版 NexT 特色",[16,130,131,132,135,136,139],{},"在 Hexo5 之後的 NexT 設置上變得很特別，你會找不到 ",[27,133,134],{},"themes\u002F_config.yml","，在此是因為改走 npm 安裝的 NexT 必須自己建立一個主題專用的 ",[27,137,138],{},"_config.yml","，依照官方說明你必須輸入以下指令(請 Hexo 根目錄輸入)",[42,141,143],{"className":44,"code":142,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"cp node_modules\u002Fhexo-theme-next\u002F_config.yml _config.next.yml\n",[27,144,145],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,146,147],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,148,142],{},[16,150,151,152,155],{},"此時就會在 Hexo 根目錄下建立一個 ",[27,153,154],{},"_config.next.yml","，而這個檔案就是我們關於主題相關的設置",[16,157,158],{},[159,160],"img",{"alt":154,"src":161},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-11-01%2013.55.03.png",[16,163,164],{},"裡面的內容基本上大同小異，因此這邊主要介紹我覺得最具特色的地方，也就是關於客製化的部分，在原本的作法我們都必須直接修改 NexT 的原始檔，因此就會導致無法更新主題，所以在一次的版本上 NexT 提供了部分頁面的客製化，其中包含了以下(截取至 _config.next.yml)",[42,166,170],{"className":167,"code":168,"language":169,"meta":47,"style":47},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","ustom_file_path:\n  #head: source\u002F_data\u002Fhead.njk # head\n  #header: source\u002F_data\u002Fheader.njk\n  #sidebar: source\u002F_data\u002Fsidebar.njk # 側邊欄\n  #postMeta: source\u002F_data\u002Fpost-meta.njk # 文章標題底下\n  #postBodyEnd: source\u002F_data\u002Fpost-body-end.njk # 文章結尾\n  #footer: source\u002F_data\u002Ffooter.njk # footer 結尾\n  #bodyEnd: source\u002F_data\u002Fbody-end.njk\n  #variable: source\u002F_data\u002Fvariables.styl\n  #mixin: source\u002F_data\u002Fmixins.styl\n  #style: source\u002F_data\u002Fstyles.styl\n","yml",[27,171,172,182,189,195,201,207,213,219,225,231,237],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,173,174,178],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,175,177],{"class":176},"sKpQp","ustom_file_path",[51,179,181],{"class":180},"sMAXC",":\n",[51,183,185],{"class":53,"line":184},2,[51,186,188],{"class":187},"sQrFR","  #head: source\u002F_data\u002Fhead.njk # head\n",[51,190,192],{"class":53,"line":191},3,[51,193,194],{"class":187},"  #header: source\u002F_data\u002Fheader.njk\n",[51,196,198],{"class":53,"line":197},4,[51,199,200],{"class":187},"  #sidebar: source\u002F_data\u002Fsidebar.njk # 側邊欄\n",[51,202,204],{"class":53,"line":203},5,[51,205,206],{"class":187},"  #postMeta: source\u002F_data\u002Fpost-meta.njk # 文章標題底下\n",[51,208,210],{"class":53,"line":209},6,[51,211,212],{"class":187},"  #postBodyEnd: source\u002F_data\u002Fpost-body-end.njk # 文章結尾\n",[51,214,216],{"class":53,"line":215},7,[51,217,218],{"class":187},"  #footer: source\u002F_data\u002Ffooter.njk # footer 結尾\n",[51,220,222],{"class":53,"line":221},8,[51,223,224],{"class":187},"  #bodyEnd: source\u002F_data\u002Fbody-end.njk\n",[51,226,228],{"class":53,"line":227},9,[51,229,230],{"class":187},"  #variable: source\u002F_data\u002Fvariables.styl\n",[51,232,234],{"class":53,"line":233},10,[51,235,236],{"class":187},"  #mixin: source\u002F_data\u002Fmixins.styl\n",[51,238,240],{"class":53,"line":239},11,[51,241,242],{"class":187},"  #style: source\u002F_data\u002Fstyles.styl\n",[16,244,245],{},"(另外附帶一提，這一次的 NexT 也將模板改成 njk)",[16,247,248],{},"相信聰明的你一看就知道我們客製化的部分就會直接放在 source 底下與以往直接修改 NexT 原始碼有很大的不同。",[16,250,251],{},"而增加的方式也變得很簡單，舉例來講我要將以下我的 Google AD 程式碼放到文章結尾處，那麼我就只需要在 post-body-end.njk 底下新增以下程式碼就可以了",[42,253,257],{"className":254,"code":255,"language":256,"meta":47,"style":47},"language-njk shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","{% if theme.google_adsense.google_ad_client_id %}\n\u003Cscript async src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpagead2.googlesyndication.com\u002Fpagead\u002Fjs\u002Fadsbygoogle.js\">\u003C\u002Fscript>\n\u003Cscript>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({\n          google_ad_client: '{{ theme.google_adsense.google_ad_client_id }}',\n          enable_page_level_ads: {{ theme.google_adsense.enable_page_level_ads }}\n     });\n\u003C\u002Fscript>\n{% endif %}\n","njk",[27,258,259,264,269,274,279,284,289,294,299],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,260,261],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,262,263],{},"{% if theme.google_adsense.google_ad_client_id %}\n",[51,265,266],{"class":53,"line":184},[51,267,268],{},"\u003Cscript async src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpagead2.googlesyndication.com\u002Fpagead\u002Fjs\u002Fadsbygoogle.js\">\u003C\u002Fscript>\n",[51,270,271],{"class":53,"line":191},[51,272,273],{},"\u003Cscript>\n",[51,275,276],{"class":53,"line":197},[51,277,278],{},"     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({\n",[51,280,281],{"class":53,"line":203},[51,282,283],{},"          google_ad_client: '{{ theme.google_adsense.google_ad_client_id }}',\n",[51,285,286],{"class":53,"line":209},[51,287,288],{},"          enable_page_level_ads: {{ theme.google_adsense.enable_page_level_ads }}\n",[51,290,291],{"class":53,"line":215},[51,292,293],{},"     });\n",[51,295,296],{"class":53,"line":221},[51,297,298],{},"\u003C\u002Fscript>\n",[51,300,301],{"class":53,"line":227},[51,302,303],{},"{% endif %}\n",[16,305,306],{},"關於 Google AD 的部分設置會針對 _config.next.yml 結尾處增加以下程式碼",[42,308,310],{"className":167,"code":309,"language":169,"meta":47,"style":47},"# Google AdSense\ngoogle_adsense:\n  enable: true\n  google_ad_client_id: #\n  enable_page_level_ads: true\n  ## siderbar_enable\n  siderbar_enable: true\n  siderbar_data_ad_slot: #\n  ## post header\n  postheader_enable: true\n  postheader_data_ad_slot: #\n  ## post footer\n  postfooter_enable: true\n  postfooter_data_ad_slot: #\n",[27,311,312,317,324,336,346,355,360,369,378,383,392,401,407,417],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,313,314],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,315,316],{"class":187},"# Google AdSense\n",[51,318,319,322],{"class":53,"line":184},[51,320,321],{"class":176},"google_adsense",[51,323,181],{"class":180},[51,325,326,329,332],{"class":53,"line":191},[51,327,328],{"class":176},"  enable",[51,330,331],{"class":180},": ",[51,333,335],{"class":334},"sCcAr","true\n",[51,337,338,341,343],{"class":53,"line":197},[51,339,340],{"class":176},"  google_ad_client_id",[51,342,331],{"class":180},[51,344,345],{"class":187},"#\n",[51,347,348,351,353],{"class":53,"line":203},[51,349,350],{"class":176},"  enable_page_level_ads",[51,352,331],{"class":180},[51,354,335],{"class":334},[51,356,357],{"class":53,"line":209},[51,358,359],{"class":187},"  ## siderbar_enable\n",[51,361,362,365,367],{"class":53,"line":215},[51,363,364],{"class":176},"  siderbar_enable",[51,366,331],{"class":180},[51,368,335],{"class":334},[51,370,371,374,376],{"class":53,"line":221},[51,372,373],{"class":176},"  siderbar_data_ad_slot",[51,375,331],{"class":180},[51,377,345],{"class":187},[51,379,380],{"class":53,"line":227},[51,381,382],{"class":187},"  ## post header\n",[51,384,385,388,390],{"class":53,"line":233},[51,386,387],{"class":176},"  postheader_enable",[51,389,331],{"class":180},[51,391,335],{"class":334},[51,393,394,397,399],{"class":53,"line":239},[51,395,396],{"class":176},"  postheader_data_ad_slot",[51,398,331],{"class":180},[51,400,345],{"class":187},[51,402,404],{"class":53,"line":403},12,[51,405,406],{"class":187},"  ## post footer\n",[51,408,410,413,415],{"class":53,"line":409},13,[51,411,412],{"class":176},"  postfooter_enable",[51,414,331],{"class":180},[51,416,335],{"class":334},[51,418,420,423,425],{"class":53,"line":419},14,[51,421,422],{"class":176},"  postfooter_data_ad_slot",[51,424,331],{"class":180},[51,426,345],{"class":187},[16,428,429,430,434],{},"觀念可以參考先前我寫的這一篇「",[102,431,433],{"href":432},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20190703\u002F893132670\u002F","替 Hexo NexT 增加 Google AdSense","」概念都是相同的，因此這一段其實還需要做調整。",[16,436,437],{},"回歸正題，透過這種方式我們就可以大幅度的客製化自己的主題並不修改到 NexT 原始碼，在主題設置上也可以比較方便，其餘的部分我就不詳細說了，其實看官方文件就很詳細囉",[16,439,440],{},[102,441,445],{"href":442,"rel":443},"https:\u002F\u002Ftheme-next.js.org\u002Fdocs\u002Fadvanced-settings\u002Fcustom-files.html",[444],"nofollow","Custom Files",[12,447,448],{"id":448},"最後",[16,450,451],{},"最後的最後我忘記補充一段，就是關於先前文章的問題，其實文章轉移很簡單，就一樣將文章原始檔整個丟到 source 就好了。",[453,454,455],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}",{"title":47,"searchDepth":184,"depth":184,"links":457},[458,459,460,461],{"id":14,"depth":184,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":184,"text":22},{"id":127,"depth":184,"text":128},{"id":448,"depth":184,"text":448},"Hexo","2020-11-01 13:21:00","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fhexo\u002F33-hexo-next","3",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F33-試著學-Hexo-番外篇之更新-NexT-主題",[462,474,475],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F","4MXE3FZsYv2e00504kWN02ci_B8TiLJFtkzLbukKuFE",{"newer":480,"older":484},{"url":481,"title":482,"date":483},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201102\u002F3342018158\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (39) - 音樂","2020-11-02 08:20:28",{"url":485,"title":486,"date":487},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201031\u002F3727169327\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (38) - TexturePacker","2020-10-31 14:56:47",[489,494,498],{"url":490,"title":491,"date":492,"readingMinutes":493},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20221030\u002F561405053\u002F","解決 Hexo 更新系統或使用 CI 部署後文章出現更新日期的問題","2022-10-30 11:52:35","2",{"url":495,"title":496,"date":497,"readingMinutes":493},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F","(32)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 Hexo","2020-10-31 14:01:51",{"url":499,"title":500,"date":501,"readingMinutes":493},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201014\u002F642399884\u002F","(31) 試著學 Hexo - 番外篇之常見問題","2020-10-14 00:00:01",1784020386162]